column5: It a done deal house in Shelburne is sold bought a much smaller place in Orangeville, movin September 30th. The new digs in the ville should suit us well all the big ticket items have been done,windows,roof,doors,kitchen,bathroom.  I like to tinker in the garden a bit and the new place has nice back and side yard.
Say hi to the hot blonde girls that work at Island Lake for me
Congrats, looks like a nice place
I'll bet that place was in 'move in' condition.  Looks like the previous owners were meticulous about their yard.  May you enjoy many great years there!
gorgeous backyard. very cozy and shaded.  I dont envy the upkeep thats going to be needed to keep it in that shape though lol. Hopefully youve got a bit of a green thumb.
So your called Rapala Boy your gender says female and you like the blond hotties at the res!!
Yes it is in move in condition not a thing to do which suits my lazy frugal side. The yard is very nice and very well maintained and there is a nice waterfall/pond maybe I`ll get me a pet Bass!
Not that there's anything wrong with that   .
